  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>我是欢乐马</span> <span>2026-03-20 07:58</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=556dbb84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FWX3IYB1YgSCiciczHgqOmveqKuYybmLaEJ76TOHfmzaeKP3HrMJ8naDbVdILryQiaGNX32c43Fd8jA1uc7a959dT8ibBQZKw2ADicOHZe3Aq13eo%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>QClaw是腾讯官方推出的桌面Agent产品，基于OpenClaw开源生态打造，核心亮点是直接打通微信。</p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;margin-top: 0 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">一句话介绍</span><span leaf=\"\">：QClaw是腾讯官方推出的桌面Agent产品，基于OpenClaw开源生态打造，核心亮点是</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接打通微信</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">——你在手机上发一句话，家里的电脑就开始干活。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">马化腾亲自站台，两周从0到1上线。我深度体验了2天，从0.0.9版本一路升级到0.1.12，见证了它的快速迭代。这篇文章，我用</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">3个完整实战案例+5个趣味体验</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，带你全面上手这只\"龙虾\"。</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 2px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);height: 1px;border: none;margin: 2em 0;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;border-bottom: 2px solid #0F4C81;margin: 2em auto 1em;color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.5em 1em;font-size: 22.4px;text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\"><span leaf=\"\">一、安装配置：5分钟搞定</span></h1>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 20.8px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 下载安装</span></h2>\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;outline: none;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-variant-alternates: inherit;font-variant-position: inherit;font-variant-emoji: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-stretch: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, &quot;Heti Hei&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;font-language-override: inherit;font-size: 16px;vertical-align: baseline;border: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.32px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">官网下载地址：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://qclaw.qq.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://qclaw.qq.com/</a></span>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100002402\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=de252b93&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FWX3IYB1YgSCtxHyBclUiavKcu09ozTtP19iaZkB0xBDQu0ibNQA9qF8wlChpzGhnxcrFSlNUYVWTybf1cIloO8ia2QTWs56ybPWiaNnVKlz3UCT4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">QClaw目前处于内测阶段，需要邀请码。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 0;color: #3f3f3f;list-style: none;padding-left: 1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"display: block;color: #3f3f3f;margin: 0.5em 8px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 下载安装包，输入内测码即可进入主界面</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"display: block;color: #3f3f3f;margin: 0.5em 8px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 启动速度极快，几乎无延迟</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 20.8px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 绑定微信（核心功能）</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100002403\" data-ratio=\"0.4601851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=82bd84e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FWX3IYB1YgSAfM1AocSRgoap2X5y7pHvl1bYDjWCdyIWHiaXSQgB31uT2MMkJXa3UI04te3QtONwB5ibGQds7rMunTNuuVBL94sic12ibtKUUjSA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">点击\"链接微信\"按钮，生成二维码 → 微信扫码 → 授权登录。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">全程不到10秒</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">绑定成功后，微信里会出现\"QClaw\"客服对话窗口。</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">所有远程操作，都在这个对话框里完成</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100002404\" data-ratio=\"1.349680170575693\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"938\" style=\"width:253px;height:341px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b42f4ff9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FWX3IYB1YgSAo5fS8kZJ6yHKsQuIzYKkvmIpMicb5RYJPDBHMBUXIhzfFzxmQE9iauFD0d4qWGTT190VJamzNNhJQykXve9boTA77XTQWTY1wU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 2px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);height: 1px;border: none;margin: 2em 0;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;border-bottom: 2px solid #0F4C81;margin: 2em auto 1em;color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.5em 1em;font-size: 22.4px;text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\"><span leaf=\"\">二、实战案例1：AI新闻定时推送</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：每天自动收集热点AI新闻，定时推送到微信。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">指令</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100002405\" data-ratio=\"1.8224598930481284\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"935\" style=\"width:322px;height:587px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f7f7b6b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FWX3IYB1YgSDuRC4SaCxJLffribYic3VvpyIGMiawz6GuNTFzdRxuOME4PicTOkKuv0qJSGzu6pYm0rpkn0KLQ00DSEIZ0tYcx2WIVrOqV2rqYd0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">QClaw执行流程</span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin-left: 0;color: #3f3f3f;padding-left: 1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"display: block;color: #3f3f3f;margin: 0.5em 8px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">检测技能</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：自动查找并安装新闻搜索相关技能</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"display: block;color: #3f3f3f;margin: 0.5em 8px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">2.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">设置定时任务</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：创建每天8:00执行的自动化流程</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"display: block;color: #3f3f3f;margin: 0.5em 8px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">3.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新闻收集</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：调用搜索能力，抓取AI领域最新动态</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"display: block;color: #3f3f3f;margin: 0.5em 8px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">4.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">整理简报</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：生成结构化内容（标题+摘要+链接）</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"display: block;color: #3f3f3f;margin: 0.5em 8px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">5.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">微信推送</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：以客服消息形式发送到微信</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">效果</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100002406\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83606814&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FWX3IYB1YgSB2dfiaUMdWd2kFteeSXoQfA8ia8jiaHN2pGLkebKQZ1jdTvBtzL5a9zichDZxzLSjibia5ibpGzngEpcYtBlu6QYoADZd2mtxEsPKePI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><strong style=\"color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">全程零配置，一句话搞定。</span></strong></p>\n   <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 2px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);height: 1px;border: none;margin: 2em 0;background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;border-bottom: 2px solid #0F4C81;margin: 2em auto 1em;color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.5em 1em;font-size: 22.4px;text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\"><span leaf=\"\">三、实战案例2：微信远程操控电脑</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是QClaw最实用的功能。人在外面，手机发指令，家里电脑立即执行。</span></p>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 20.8px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">子任务1：文件整理</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1e